<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grant Writing Resources</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <style>
        
        body {
            background-color: #1e1e2f; 
            color: #eaeaea; 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header.header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            background-color: #27273a;
            color: #f9f9f9;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        section {
            margin: 2rem auto;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: #2a2a3e;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ffd700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .tips .tip-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tip-card {
            background-color: #3a3a54;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            width: 250px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tip-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .tip-card i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ff6f61;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tip-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tip-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        section.guides ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        section.guides li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        section.guides a {
            color: #00aaff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        section.guides a:hover {
            color: #ffa500;
        }

        footer.footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #27273a;
            color: #bdbdbd;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>Grant Writing Resources</h1>
        <p>Your go-to place for improving your grant-writing skills.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="tips animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h2>Top Tips for Writing Grants</h2>
        <div class="tip-cards">
            <div class="tip-card animate__animated animate__zoomIn animate__delay-1s">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                <h3>Understand Your Audience</h3>
                <p>Learn about the funder's goals and tailor your grant proposal to align with their mission.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip-card">
                <i class="fas fa-pen-fancy"></i>
                <h3>Be Clear and Concise</h3>
                <p>Write in simple, jargon-free language to ensure your message is easily understood.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip-card">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h3>Focus on Impact</h3>
                <p>Highlight measurable outcomes and how your project addresses key issues.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="guides">
        <h2>Comprehensive Guides</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.india.gov.in/my-government/documents/demand-grant">Step-by-Step Grant Proposal Guide</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.clicktime.com/blog/how-to-write-a-grant-budget-to-win-your-dream-grant">Budget Planning for Grant Writing</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/crafting-effective-budget-narratives-grant-success-yilmaz-ozmen-lhspf">Crafting Effective Grant Narratives</a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 Grant Writing Support Tool. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>